T1  - The Relationship Among Perceptual Similarity, Sex, and Performance Ratings in Manager-Subordinate Dyads
AU  - Pulakos, Elaine D.
AU  - Wexley, Kenneth N.
Y1  - 1983/03/01
PY  - 1983
DA  - 1983/03/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256139
