JO  - AMJ
SP  - 45
EP  - 63
VL  - 26
IS  - 1
PB  - Academy of Management
N2  - Six instruments previously used to assess Perrow's dimensions of work unit technology are evaluated. The findings suggest convergent validity across measures of the analyzability and exceptions dimensions. A new instrument is developed that has somewhat greater ability to differentiate among work units and that improves the fit between the theoretical constructs and their empirical measures.
AB  - Six instruments previously used to assess Perrow's dimensions of work unit technology are evaluated. The findings suggest convergent validity across measures of the analyzability and exceptions dimensions. A new instrument is developed that has somewhat greater ability to differentiate among work units and that improves the fit between the theoretical constructs and their empirical measures.
